article_title: Disney Offers Full-Time Positions To Park Staff As Obamacare Starts
article_text: Walt Disney Co. (DIS) is offering full-time positions to 427 part-time employees at Walt Disney World in Florida who worked enough hours to qualify for health benefits under the Affordable Care Act.
